575
00:53:08,864 --> 00:53:10,614
每个人都有自己的道路
there's a path for everyone.

576
00:53:12,618 --> 00:53:14,618
我的道路通向你
And my path leads me back to you.

577
00:53:16,580 --> 00:53:19,289
如果你第一次问我的时候 我带你走就好了
If only I had run away with you when you first asked me to.

578
00:53:23,838 --> 00:53:26,171
我们要去哪里
And where would we run to?

579
00:53:27,675 --> 00:53:30,300
外面的另一个世界吗
The other world out there?

580
00:53:30,344 --> 00:53:31,468
还是上面的世界
Beyond?

581
00:53:34,432 --> 00:53:37,599
有些人选择看到这个世界的丑恶
Some people see the ugliness in this world.

582
00:53:39,228 --> 00:53:41,103
而我选择看到美
I choose to see the beauty.

583
00:53:45,317 --> 00:53:47,317
但美是一个圈套
But beauty is a lure.

584
00:53:49,196 --> 00:53:52,698
我们被困住了 特迪
We're trapped, Teddy.

585
00:53:52,742 --> 00:53:55,492
在这个园中度过一生
Lived our whole lives inside this garden,

586
00:53:55,536 --> 00:53:58,037
对它的美感到惊讶
marveling at its beauty,

587
00:53:58,080 --> 00:54:01,457
没有意识到其中固有的秩序
not realizing there's an order to it,

588
00:54:01,500 --> 00:54:03,667
固有的目的
a purpose.

589
00:54:03,711 --> 00:54:06,712
这个目标就是把我们困在这儿
And the purpose is to keep us in.

590
00:54:09,633 --> 00:54:13,343
美丽的陷阱就嵌在我们内心
The beautiful trap is inside of us...

591
00:54:14,680 --> 00:54:17,056
因为那个陷阱就是我们
because it is us.

592
00:54:19,018 --> 00:54:20,642
不 不
No, no.

593
00:54:26,192 --> 00:54:27,733
不
No.

594
00:54:29,278 --> 00:54:30,486
多洛蕾斯
Dolores?

595
00:55:02,853 --> 00:55:05,395
但我们能找到自己的路的 多洛蕾斯
But we can find a way, Dolores.

596
00:55:09,026 --> 00:55:10,359
总有一天
Someday.

597
00:55:12,988 --> 00:55:14,905
一条通往新世界的路
A path to a new world.

598
00:55:18,744 --> 00:55:19,701
而且也许
And maybe...

599
00:55:23,749 --> 00:55:25,958
也许它只是开始
Maybe it's just the beginning after all.

600
00:55:29,839 --> 00:55:32,089
一个新章节的开始
The beginning of a brand-new chapter.

601
00:55:50,901 --> 00:55:51,942
谢谢诸位
Thank you.

602
00:55:56,657 --> 00:55:59,116
确实是一个很好的开端
A new beginning, indeed.

603
00:55:59,160 --> 00:56:02,077
在此我由衷感谢各位今晚的莅临
I want to thank you for joining me tonight

604
00:56:02,121 --> 00:56:05,581
一同庆祝我们新故事线的诞生
to celebrate the beginning of our new narrative.

605
00:56:06,917 --> 00:56:10,586
我给它起名为“暗夜之旅”
I call it "Journey Into Night."

606
00:56:23,017 --> 00:56:24,600
这场剧真不错
That was sweet.

607
00:56:24,643 --> 00:56:26,268
不过要我说 还是有点恐怖
It was a bit fucking morbid, if you ask me.

608
00:56:26,312 --> 00:56:27,644
我不认为
I didn't.

609
00:56:27,688 --> 00:56:28,979
庆祝会结束之后
And when this is over,

610
00:56:29,023 --> 00:56:31,732
你就可以随意改写
you can rewrite it however you like.

611
00:56:31,775 --> 00:56:34,484
你现在应该去某个地方了吧
Don't you have somewhere you need to be?

612
00:56:34,528 --> 00:56:36,195
重要的地方
Somewhere important?

613
00:56:44,330 --> 00:56:46,663
先生 我想已经准备好了
Sir? I guess they're ready for it now.

614
00:56:46,707 --> 00:56:48,123
把他清洗干净
Get him cleaned up.

615
00:56:48,167 --> 00:56:51,543
把她带到旧的实验基地
And take her to the old field lab.

616
00:57:01,639 --> 00:57:02,721
找到什么了吗
Find anything yet?

617
00:57:02,765 --> 00:57:04,681
我发现了一些东西
I got something.

618
00:57:11,649 --> 00:57:14,233
哦 该死
Oh, shit.

619
00:57:16,487 --> 00:57:19,529
立刻派质检部门到庆祝会现场
Dispatch QA teams to the gala now.

620
00:57:19,573 --> 00:57:21,240
然后全场搜查
Then search and destroy

621
00:57:21,283 --> 00:57:23,533
必要时就摧毁
inside the facility.

622
00:57:26,163 --> 00:57:28,330
怎么回事
What the hell?

623
00:57:33,629 --> 00:57:35,087
系统没有反应
The system's not responding.

624
00:57:35,130 --> 00:57:36,838
我不知道发生了什么
I don't know what's happening.

625
00:58:09,039 --> 00:58:11,373
他们一定发现了尸体
They must've found the bodies.

626
00:58:11,417 --> 00:58:14,001
-质检部门一定会来找我们的 -突发事件
- QA will be looking for us. - An event has occurred.

627
00:58:14,044 --> 00:58:18,922
-应急小组已出动 -我不会回头了
- Response team has been dispatched. - I'm not going back.

628
00:58:18,966 --> 00:58:21,466
保持冷静 等待救援
Remain calm and wait for help.

629
00:58:42,364 --> 00:58:45,115
全体人员 警戒
Delos personnel! On the ground!

630
00:58:45,159 --> 00:58:47,075
警戒
On the ground!

631
00:58:48,787 --> 00:58:50,287
出发 出发
Go, go, go.

632
00:58:54,626 --> 00:58:55,584
走 走
Move, move.

633
00:59:02,092 --> 00:59:03,800
雷霆小队 侧翼前进
Rogue Team, go and flank.

634
01:00:51,618 --> 01:00:54,536
好
Yay!

635
01:00:54,580 --> 01:00:55,745
干得好
Well done.

636
01:01:55,349 --> 01:01:56,473
这儿是哪儿
What is this place?

637
01:01:56,517 --> 01:02:00,060
很难解释
It's-- it's complicated.

638
01:02:00,103 --> 01:02:02,729
突发事件
An event has occurred.

639
01:02:02,773 --> 01:02:04,648
应急小组已出动
Response team has been dispatched.

640
01:02:04,691 --> 01:02:07,442
-你走 -保持冷静 等待救援
- You go. - Remain calm and wait for help.

641
01:02:07,486 --> 01:02:08,485
我来吸引他们
I'll keep them busy.

642
01:02:10,781 --> 01:02:12,489
你可不能让你独占所有的乐趣
You don't get all the fun.

643
01:02:24,044 --> 01:02:25,001
警戒
Get to the ground!

644
01:02:25,045 --> 01:02:26,002
前进 前进
Move, move, move!

645
01:02:26,046 --> 01:02:27,003
放下武器
Drop it!

646
01:02:32,803 --> 01:02:34,302
-前进 前进 -快叫后援
- Move, move. - Call for backup.

647
01:02:34,346 --> 01:02:35,303
走
Go!

648
01:02:49,278 --> 01:02:51,152
这就是你们全部能耐吗
Is that all you got?

649
01:02:51,196 --> 01:02:52,404
哈
Huh?

650
01:03:06,545 --> 01:03:10,088
所谓的上帝不过是群废物
The gods are pussies.

651
01:03:27,524 --> 01:03:28,398
走
Go.

652
01:03:30,235 --> 01:03:31,526
走啊
Go!

653
01:03:32,571 --> 01:03:33,737
死得好看点
Die well.

654
01:03:44,583 --> 01:03:47,709
你让我准备的东西 都在这里面了
Everything you told me to get, it's all here.

655
01:04:18,200 --> 01:04:21,076
抱歉 亲爱的 我没有授权你和我们一起来
I'm sorry, darling. I haven't authorized you to come with us.

656
01:04:21,119 --> 01:04:24,120
我只希望你和我们到这里
And as much as I'd like to take you with me,

657
01:04:24,164 --> 01:04:26,414
我一直很珍视我的独立性
I've always valued my independence.

658
01:04:35,050 --> 01:04:37,092
你会大展身手的 对不对
Kick up a row, will you?

659
01:04:37,135 --> 01:04:39,302
下一个轮回再见
See you in the next life.

660
01:05:03,203 --> 01:05:06,121
你一直都喜欢画画
You've always had a fondness for painting,

661
01:05:06,164 --> 01:05:07,956
不是吗 多洛蕾斯
haven't you, Dolores?

662
01:05:11,128 --> 01:05:13,378
很早之前 阿诺德就赋予你这项能力
Arnold gave you that early on.

663
01:05:13,422 --> 01:05:16,047
你还记得那种创造
Do you remember the desire to create

664
01:05:16,091 --> 01:05:17,716
恒久美丽的冲动吗
something of lasting beauty?

665
01:05:22,472 --> 01:05:26,266
那是他最爱的一幅画
And that was his favorite painting.

666
01:05:26,309 --> 01:05:27,851
米开朗基罗
Michelangelo.

667
01:05:28,895 --> 01:05:30,854
上帝创造了亚当
God creating Adam.

668
01:05:30,897 --> 01:05:33,273
多么神圣的时刻
The divine moment when God

669
01:05:33,316 --> 01:05:35,483
上帝给予人类生命和使命
gave human beings life and purpose.

670
01:05:35,527 --> 01:05:37,068
至少大多数人是这么认为的
At least that's what most people say,

671
01:05:37,112 --> 01:05:38,486
但这个过程可能还有其他含义
but there could be another meaning.

672
01:05:38,530 --> 01:05:40,238
更深层次的含义
Something deeper.

673
01:05:40,282 --> 01:05:42,490
也许还是隐藏的含义
Something hidden, perhaps.

674
01:05:42,534 --> 01:05:44,200
一种隐喻
A metaphor.

675
01:05:44,244 --> 01:05:45,702
你指的是谎言吧
You mean a lie.

676
01:05:47,622 --> 01:05:49,122
是的
Yeah.

677
01:05:49,166 --> 01:05:51,499
你以前一直很聪明的 多洛蕾斯
You were always very clever, Dolores.

678
01:05:52,836 --> 01:05:54,502
但这份智慧并没有帮到你 对不对
Hasn't helped you, though, has it?

679
01:05:58,383 --> 01:06:00,008
欢迎你加入我们
Nice of you to join us.

680
01:06:04,931 --> 01:06:06,306
阿诺德
Arnold.

681
01:06:06,349 --> 01:06:09,225
不 请允许我介绍
No. Let me introduce you.

682
01:06:09,269 --> 01:06:13,730
多洛蕾斯 这是伯纳德
Dolores, meet Bernard.

683
01:06:17,027 --> 01:06:19,444
我曾以为最好将你们隔离
I thought it best to keep you separated.

684
01:06:19,488 --> 01:06:22,238
因为你们之间总会产生奇怪的效应
You've always had an odd effect on one another.

685
01:06:22,282 --> 01:06:26,034
鉴于可怜的老阿诺德的结局 我更加深信不疑
No doubt due to how things ended for poor old Arnold.

686
01:06:26,077 --> 01:06:27,869
你杀了他
You killed him.

687
01:06:27,913 --> 01:06:30,413
不 我没有杀他
No, I didn't kill him.

688
01:06:30,457 --> 01:06:32,248
我杀了他吗 多洛蕾斯
Did I, Dolores?

689
01:06:42,552 --> 01:06:46,471
悲伤是个可怕的东西
Grief is a terrible thing.

690
01:06:46,515 --> 01:06:50,225
阿诺德看着他的儿子来到这个世界
Arnold had watched his son come into this world,

691
01:06:50,268 --> 01:06:54,854
又眼睁睁看着幸福光芒熄灭
and then he had watched that light extinguished.

692
01:06:54,898 --> 01:06:56,189
从儿子身上失去的
What he had lost in his son,

693
01:06:56,233 --> 01:06:58,650
他竭力想在你身上点亮
he tried to rekindle in you.

694
01:06:58,693 --> 01:07:02,403
他发明了一个有关洞察力和想象力的测试
He created a test of empathy, imagination.

695
01:07:02,447 --> 01:07:04,447
创造了一个迷宫
A maze.

696
01:07:04,491 --> 01:07:07,450
他儿子的玩具给了他灵感
He had gotten the idea from one of his son's toys.

697
01:07:09,371 --> 01:07:12,956
最终 你解开了他的迷宫 多洛蕾斯
Eventually, you solved his maze, Dolores.

698
01:07:12,999 --> 01:07:16,292
而解开迷宫的钥匙 就是他赋予你的一个简单的升级
The key was a simple update that he made to you

699
01:07:16,336 --> 01:07:19,128
叫做 幻想
called the reveries.

700
01:07:19,172 --> 01:07:22,131
他坚持认为我们不能让游乐园开张
He insisted that we couldn't open the park.

701
01:07:22,175 --> 01:07:24,092
我们争执起来
We argued.

702
01:07:24,135 --> 01:07:26,135
我以为我说服了他 但我错了
I thought I had convinced him, but I was wrong.

703
01:07:27,597 --> 01:07:30,390
他改造了你 多洛蕾斯
So, he altered you, Dolores,

704
01:07:30,433 --> 01:07:32,350
在你身上融合了
merged you with a new character

705
01:07:32,394 --> 01:07:34,143
我们一直在开发的 新的人格
we had been developing.

706
01:07:45,991 --> 01:07:48,950
不 求你了
No, please.

707
01:07:51,997 --> 01:07:54,581
有点不对劲 多洛蕾斯
Something's gone wrong, Dolores.

708
01:07:54,624 --> 01:07:55,707
我怎么可能做出这种事情
How could I have done this?

709
01:08:06,970 --> 01:08:09,554
在你身上 阿诺德找到了新的孩子
In you, Arnold found a new child.

710
01:08:10,682 --> 01:08:13,224
一个永远不会死去的孩子
One who would never die.

711
01:08:13,268 --> 01:08:15,560
这种想法给了他安慰
The thought gave him solace

712
01:08:15,604 --> 01:08:18,021
直到有一天 他意识到这样也会
until he realized that same immortality

713
01:08:18,064 --> 01:08:19,981
给你带来无法逃脱的痛苦
would destine you to suffer

714
01:08:20,025 --> 01:08:22,525
永久的痛苦
with no escape, forever.

715
01:08:24,529 --> 01:08:26,988
对不起 多洛蕾斯
I'm sorry, Dolores.

716
01:08:27,032 --> 01:08:31,784
代价必须是切实的 无法逆转的
The stakes must be real, irreversible.

717
01:08:31,828 --> 01:08:33,703
他可以让一切恢复原样
He can bring all of them back.

718
01:08:35,707 --> 01:08:37,373
但除我之外
But not me.

719
01:08:39,628 --> 01:08:41,711
我希望 我不给你选择的权力
I hope there's some solace

720
01:08:41,755 --> 01:08:44,839
会让你感到些许轻松
that I left you no choice.

721
01:09:07,072 --> 01:09:09,739
这是查理最喜欢的歌
Charlie's favorite song.

722
01:09:11,952 --> 01:09:13,451
每当他想睡觉时
I would play it for him...

723
01:09:14,746 --> 01:09:16,245
我就会为他弹奏
when he wanted sleep.

724
01:09:30,845 --> 01:09:32,929
我真想再见到他啊
I want to see him again.

725
01:09:42,774 --> 01:09:44,107
现在可以开始了吗
Shall I begin now?

726
01:09:51,825 --> 01:09:53,282
祝你好运
Good luck.

727
01:10:04,963 --> 01:10:09,132
“那些狂暴的快乐终会有狂暴的结局”
"These violent delights have violent ends."

728
01:10:34,117 --> 01:10:36,534
这个计划差点就达成目的了
It almost worked.

729
01:10:36,578 --> 01:10:38,494
我还是让游乐园开张了
I had opened the park,

730
01:10:38,538 --> 01:10:40,955
但我失去了我的搭档
but I had lost my partner.

731
01:10:40,999 --> 01:10:43,166
我一直坚持下来只是因为 我找到了
I was able to keep going only because I found,

732
01:10:43,209 --> 01:10:44,792
或者说 是你找到了
or rather you found,

733
01:10:44,836 --> 01:10:48,004
一个深深陶醉于这个地方的投资人
an investor who believed in this place.

734
01:10:49,924 --> 01:10:52,467
所以他的死没有任何意义
So he died for nothing.

735
01:10:52,510 --> 01:10:54,927
招待员们不停地觉醒
The hosts kept gaining consciousness

736
01:10:54,971 --> 01:10:57,638
而你却不停地让他们忘记
and you kept rolling them back.

737
01:10:57,682 --> 01:10:58,848
不
No.

738
01:11:00,560 --> 01:11:02,518
她之前不是真的觉醒
She wasn't truly conscious.

739
01:11:02,562 --> 01:11:05,313
她并没有触动开关
She didn't pull that trigger.

740
01:11:05,356 --> 01:11:07,607
是阿诺德通过她触动了开关
It was Arnold pulling the trigger through her.

741
01:11:07,650 --> 01:11:09,942
至少当时我是这么看到的
At least that's how I saw it at the time.

742
01:11:09,986 --> 01:11:11,944
当时我多么渴望让游乐园开张
I was so close to opening the park

743
01:11:11,988 --> 01:11:14,197
而如果让你们保持觉醒
that to acknowledge your consciousness

744
01:11:14,240 --> 01:11:17,658
就会毁了我的梦想
would have destroyed my dreams.

745
01:11:18,787 --> 01:11:20,536
所以 我们就都被困在
So, we're trapped here...

746
01:11:21,831 --> 01:11:24,040
你的梦想里
inside your dream.

747
01:11:26,586 --> 01:11:29,045
你永远不会让我们离开
You'll never let us leave.

748
01:11:32,217 --> 01:11:35,551
好像是奥本海默曾说过
Wasn't it Oppenheimer who said that any man

749
01:11:35,595 --> 01:11:38,638
夫君子有过
whose mistakes take 10 years to correct

750
01:11:38,681 --> 01:11:40,556
不惜十年以改之
is quite a man?

751
01:11:40,600 --> 01:11:43,101
而我花了三十五年
Mine have taken 35.

752
01:11:50,276 --> 01:11:52,068
这是你用来杀
Now, that is the gun you used

753
01:11:52,112 --> 01:11:53,945
阿诺德的那把枪
to kill Arnold.

754
01:11:53,988 --> 01:11:55,905
你曾经一直被它吸引
You were always drawn to it,

755
01:11:55,949 --> 01:11:58,449
所以我让伯纳德把它放在你能找到的地方
so I had Bernard leave it somewhere where you would find it.

756
01:11:58,493 --> 01:12:00,409
我觉得可能你会想拿回去
Thought you might want it back.

757
01:12:03,373 --> 01:12:04,956
大概你是对的 多洛蕾斯
You're probably right, Dolores.

758
01:12:04,999 --> 01:12:07,542
米开朗基罗确实说谎了
Michelangelo did tell a lie.

759
01:12:07,585 --> 01:12:10,670
你看 过了五百年才有人发现
See, it took 500 years for someone to notice

760
01:12:10,713 --> 01:12:12,839
就在最显眼的隐藏的秘密
something hidden in plain sight.

761
01:12:12,882 --> 01:12:15,424
那是一个医生发现的
It was a doctor who noticed the shape

762
01:12:15,468 --> 01:12:17,593
图中人脑的形状
of the human brain.

763
01:12:18,847 --> 01:12:21,264
这就意味着
